io.github.jonestimd.swing.window

Class WindowEventPublisher<E extends WindowInfo>

  • java.lang.Object
    • io.github.jonestimd.swing.window.WindowEventPublisher<E>

  • public class WindowEventPublisher<E extends WindowInfo>
extends java.lang.Object
    Publishes ApplicationWindowEvents to registered WindowEventListeners.

    Note: This class is not thread-safe. It is intended for use only on the AWT event thread.

    See Also:
    FrameManager, FrameAction, WindowEventListener
